{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405340/extras/intro.gif?t=1735420234\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>HOW LONG CAN YOU SURVIVE?</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Megabonk is a roguelike survival game where you must fight your way through hordes of enemies and bosses in randomly generated maps. Grab loot on the way, level up your character, upgrade your weapons and survive for as long as you can! How far can you make it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405340/extras/hordes.gif?t=1735420234\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>UPGRADE &amp; GET JUICED</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeat enemies and pick up XP to level up! The more enemies you defeat, the more XP you get. Yeah that's pretty obvious I guess. Anyway, each upgrade offer is random and will vary in rarity, which makes each run unique!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405340/extras/leveling.gif?t=1735420234\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>UNLOCK CHARACTERS, WEAPONS &amp; ITEMS</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete challenges in-game to unlock:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weapons and Tomes</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Characters with unique abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Items offering different synergies and powers</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405340/extras/skate.gif?t=1735420234\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>UNLOCK NEW MAPS AND AREAS</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the stage boss, defeat them, and unlock the next area of the map! Each map offers 3 tiers of stages, each exponentially harder than the previous one. Every stage is randomly generated, so you will have to adapt. Can you reach the boss at the final stage?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405340/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735420234","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405340/page.bg.jpg?t=1735420234","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405340/bb58c09f358e139ee33eeb502a3f66bd228395b9/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735420234","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405340/bb58c09f358e139ee33eeb502a3f66bd228395b9/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735420234","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25},{"description":"Steam Timeline","id":63}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405340/extras/intro.gif?t=1735420234\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>HOW LONG CAN YOU SURVIVE?</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Megabonk is a roguelike survival game where you must fight your way through hordes of enemies and bosses in randomly generated maps. Grab loot on the way, level up your character, upgrade your weapons and survive for as long as you can! How far can you make it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/